    <p><%= link_to "Book a prestige Yacht now!", yachts_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
  </div>

</div>
<div class="main container">
  <h3 class="featured">Succeed with Prestige Worldwide</h3>
  <p> Prestige Worldwide was founded in 2021. In the beginning, their were two brothers and best friends, who built a small
